Title: EazyAgro Wildlife-Friendly Bird Netting – 30 GSM
Description:
EazyAgro Wildlife-Friendly Bird Netting

EazyAgro Wildlife-Friendly Bird Netting is designed to protect crops from bird damage while ensuring bird safety. Manufactured from premium UV-stabilized High-Density Polyethylene (HDPE), this net provides reliable coverage without harming wildlife.

The 4.9mm × 4.9mm mesh size creates an effective barrier against birds while reducing the risk of entanglement. With a lightweight 30 GSM construction, it is easy to handle, install, and remove, making it ideal for orchards, farms, vineyards, and home gardens.

Available in high-visibility white and black colors, this netting offers flexibility for different environments and crop types.

KEY FEATURES

  • Wildlife-friendly & bird-safe design
  • Material: UV-stabilized premium HDPE
  • Weight: 30 GSM (Lightweight & durable)
  • Mesh size: 4.9mm × 4.9mm
  • Protects crops without harming birds
  • Allows airflow, sunlight & rain
  • Easy to install, remove & store
  • Suitable for repeated seasonal use

APPLICATIONS

  • Fruit trees & orchards
  • Vineyards
  • Vegetable farms
  • Home gardens
  • Nurseries

WHY CHOOSE EAZYAGRO BIRD NETTING?

  • Wildlife-friendly crop protection
  • Premium UV-stabilized HDPE
  • Lightweight, strong & reusable
  • Suitable for commercial & home use
